value: Breeds in southern Europe to Rumania, Poland and west Siberia to the Ob Valley, south to northern Africa (Morocco and Algeria) , Persia, Turke- stan, Kashmir, the Pamirs and southern Tibet. Winters in the Mediter- ranean region, Nile Valley, Persian Gulf, Arakan and Burma.
